Dialogue: 0,00:01:39.54,00:01:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,00:01:48.59,00:01:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是死人世界吗
Dialogue: 0,00:01:52.41,00:01:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我们你们要去哪
Dialogue: 0,00:01:55.66,00:01:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像有什么在拉着他们前进
Dialogue: 0,00:02:04.15,00:02:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘  够了
Dialogue: 0,00:02:06.58,00:02:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在干什么
Dialogue: 0,00:02:13.27,00:02:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,00:02:14.98,00:02:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家的精灵都哪去了
Dialogue: 0,00:02:17.07,00:02:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去过很多没有精灵的世界了
Dialogue: 0,00:02:18.75,00:02:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我兜里来  我们没事的
Dialogue: 0,00:02:20.83,00:02:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有些人该有精灵  但却没有
Dialogue: 0,00:02:31.30,00:02:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没事吧
Dialogue: 0,00:02:33.65,00:02:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没事
Dialogue: 0,00:02:35.86,00:02:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是没事
Dialogue: 0,00:02:42.78,00:02:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你见过那个吗  -没有
Dialogue: 0,00:02:47.34,00:02:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来错地方了吗
Dialogue: 0,00:02:50.43,00:02:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是这里
Dialogue: 0,00:02:51.81,00:02:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是  走吧
Dialogue: 0,00:03:45.38,00:03:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,00:03:48.17,00:03:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,00:03:54.15,00:03:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,00:03:55.95,00:03:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴再次见到你
Dialogue: 0,00:03:58.90,00:04:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉主教  库尔特夫人回来了
Dialogue: 0,00:05:58.42,00:06:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  这很好
Dialogue: 0,00:06:04.95,00:06:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  站住
Dialogue: 0,00:06:06.86,00:06:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人  站住
Dialogue: 0,00:06:11.47,00:06:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: 0,00:06:13.15,00:06:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我说你们呢
Dialogue: 0,00:06:15.51,00:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没死
Dialogue: 0,00:06:19.59,00:06:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个意外
Dialogue: 0,00:06:20.38,00:06:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人追我们
Dialogue: 0,00:06:21.67,00:06:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知怎么就来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,00:06:23.44,00:06:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们没死  就不能来
Dialogue: 0,00:06:27.26,00:06:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着
Dialogue: 0,00:06:28.87,00:06:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了很远了
Dialogue: 0,00:06:30.23,00:06:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得找到我的朋友  不然就太迟了
Dialogue: 0,00:06:32.39,00:06:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是被人追赶
Dialogue: 0,00:06:34.91,00:06:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又是找朋友
Dialogue: 0,00:06:36.83,00:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里是找不到的  撒谎
Dialogue: 0,00:06:41.86,00:06:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去32号等候区
Dialogue: 0,00:06:44.59,00:06:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他们这个
Dialogue: 0,00:06:55.02,00:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要等多久
Dialogue: 0,00:06:57.75,00:06:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是等到你们死
Dialogue: 0,00:07:03.59,00:07:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,00:07:09.86,00:07:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写了什么
Dialogue: 0,00:07:15.78,00:07:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是这里
Dialogue: 0,00:07:17.54,00:07:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得找到那片湖  然后渡过去
Dialogue: 0,00:07:23.51,00:07:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我们上次的见面没留下什么长久的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,00:07:29.61,00:07:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想保护我女儿
Dialogue: 0,00:07:33.59,00:07:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上次说话时  你还很健谈呢
Dialogue: 0,00:07:36.46,00:07:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了那么多好听的话
Dialogue: 0,00:07:38.21,00:07:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么逃走啊  愚蠢啊  错误啊
Dialogue: 0,00:07:42.26,00:07:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是主教跟你说的  我知道
Dialogue: 0,00:07:44.53,00:07:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是庭长神父
Dialogue: 0,00:07:46.74,00:07:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -他不是主教了
Dialogue: 0,00:07:49.30,00:07:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是庭长神父了
Dialogue: 0,00:07:51.67,00:07:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是他说的  是我说的
Dialogue: 0,00:07:55.46,00:07:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我见过你这样的执迷
Dialogue: 0,00:07:57.95,00:07:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,00:08:00.03,00:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你没见过
Dialogue: 0,00:08:02.74,00:08:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你就不理解信仰
Dialogue: 0,00:08:05.25,00:08:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈梅兹神父  你太年轻了
Dialogue: 0,00:08:08.23,00:08:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我们不知道你要回我们这里来吗
Dialogue: 0,00:08:13.63,00:08:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你属于这里
Dialogue: 0,00:08:16.54,00:08:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很难判断
Dialogue: 0,00:08:18.02,00:08:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教会当局知道什么  不知道什么
Dialogue: 0,00:08:22.26,00:08:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信仰总碍事
Dialogue: 0,00:08:34.55,00:08:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,00:08:35.47,00:08:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-戈梅兹神父  我带来了  -是我  休
Dialogue: 0,00:08:38.95,00:08:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是现在只有叫你"庭长神父"你才应了
Dialogue: 0,00:08:42.78,00:08:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们进去
Dialogue: 0,00:08:46.26,00:08:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,00:08:53.22,00:08:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先请
Dialogue: 0,00:09:05.27,00:09:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库尔特夫人
Dialogue: 0,00:09:10.22,00:09:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子要留下吗
Dialogue: 0,00:09:13.35,00:09:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  戈梅兹神父
Dialogue: 0,00:09:20.91,00:09:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  那就我们两个了
Dialogue: 0,00:10:07.31,00:10:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你被捕了  这不用说  -真让人失望
Dialogue: 0,00:10:09.63,00:10:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-因为有意隐瞒...  -不用了
Dialogue: 0,00:10:12.35,00:10:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我是来帮忙的  -你阻止了我们找到夏娃
Dialogue: 0,00:10:15.82,00:10:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容我说完
Dialogue: 0,00:10:18.91,00:10:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是自愿来的
Dialogue: 0,00:10:21.90,00:10:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一从阿斯里尔的堡垒逃出来  我就来了
Dialogue: 0,00:10:24.94,00:10:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看我的衣服  休
Dialogue: 0,00:10:28.07,00:10:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至带来了一件他的技术
Dialogue: 0,00:10:29.69,00:10:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你的院士会乐意研究一番
Dialogue: 0,00:10:32.63,00:10:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-只有那孩子才是重要的  -我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,00:10:37.73,00:10:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理仪说的很明白  她的身份
Dialogue: 0,00:10:41.55,00:10:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及她会带来什么
Dialogue: 0,00:10:45.99,00:10:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在自残吗
Dialogue: 0,00:10:55.27,00:10:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你当上了主教  那是为了赢得你的信任
Dialogue: 0,00:11:00.15,00:11:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-而你却背叛了我  -我背叛你
Dialogue: 0,00:11:04.63,00:11:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她就是罪孽  -不
Dialogue: 0,00:11:08.55,00:11:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有这个潜质  这我知道
Dialogue: 0,00:11:11.22,00:11:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-而我自有办法  -你才没有
Dialogue: 0,00:11:13.42,00:11:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她不走上危险的道路
Dialogue: 0,00:11:15.02,00:11:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你的谎言很卑劣  -你毁了一切
Dialogue: 0,00:11:28.75,00:11:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自以为庇佑她远离了什么危险
Dialogue: 0,00:11:36.14,00:11:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸园的陷落
Dialogue: 0,00:11:38.14,00:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为夏娃的诞生  而是因为她被诱惑
Dialogue: 0,00:11:42.91,00:11:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上存在一个诱惑者  毒蛇
Dialogue: 0,00:11:47.24,00:11:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要避免他们相见
Dialogue: 0,00:11:50.58,00:11:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到了她  还有那男孩  一切都在掌握
Dialogue: 0,00:11:54.59,00:11:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你派来了军队  把他们吓跑了
Dialogue: 0,00:12:04.02,00:12:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉·帕维尔跟你说刀的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,00:12:10.47,00:12:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强大到可以杀死权威者的武器
Dialogue: 0,00:12:16.06,00:12:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄断了那把刀
Dialogue: 0,00:12:20.67,00:12:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我驯服了它
Dialogue: 0,00:12:23.70,00:12:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要低估我仍能为你做的事
Dialogue: 0,00:12:28.78,00:12:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我可以像以前那样为你进言
Dialogue: 0,00:12:31.55,00:12:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精力应付需要打的仗
Dialogue: 0,00:12:34.11,00:12:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把莱拉和她的诱惑交给我
Dialogue: 0,00:12:37.35,00:12:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯里尔还在找那女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,00:12:41.99,00:12:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他对她从来都没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,00:12:49.50,00:12:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把刀吸引过他
Dialogue: 0,00:12:51.82,00:12:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在它断了  他只想要他的战争
Dialogue: 0,00:12:57.19,00:13:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他作战的方式  休
Dialogue: 0,00:13:01.26,00:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,00:13:07.35,00:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能眼看着他杀了一个天使
Dialogue: 0,00:13:14.14,00:13:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使
Dialogue: 0,00:13:19.83,00:13:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有天使找到了阿斯里尔
Dialogue: 0,00:13:23.70,00:13:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,00:13:28.87,00:13:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他居然伤害天使
Dialogue: 0,00:13:30.47,00:13:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是人挡杀人  佛挡杀佛
Dialogue: 0,00:13:33.62,00:13:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我  他是个疯子
Dialogue: 0,00:13:35.63,00:13:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我来找你  休
Dialogue: 0,00:13:38.79,00:13:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你贡献我的力量
Dialogue: 0,00:13:40.82,00:13:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要站在我们这边吗
Dialogue: 0,00:13:44.10,00:13:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对抗阿斯里尔
Dialogue: 0,00:13:47.15,00:13:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对抗尘埃
Dialogue: 0,00:13:50.55,00:13:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怀疑我吗
Dialogue: 0,00:13:52.47,00:13:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时你的忠心难以猜透  玛丽莎
Dialogue: 0,00:13:58.27,00:13:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拥有我的心灵
Dialogue: 0,00:14:01.19,00:14:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体  我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,00:14:06.30,00:14:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感谢权威者
Dialogue: 0,00:14:10.26,00:14:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有你来带领教会当局
Dialogue: 0,00:14:13.10,00:14:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是斯特罗克主教
Dialogue: 0,00:14:19.58,00:14:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本禁不住诱惑
Dialogue: 0,00:14:22.78,00:14:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你  你的节制很了不起
Dialogue: 0,00:14:50.07,00:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住我们一起做了什么
Dialogue: 0,00:14:54.02,00:14:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的生命纠缠在一起
Dialogue: 0,00:15:22.07,00:15:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文件
Dialogue: 0,00:15:29.95,00:15:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去507号等候区
Dialogue: 0,00:15:33.26,00:15:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-又是一个等候区  -不是又一个等候区
Dialogue: 0,00:15:36.87,00:15:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,507号等候区  507
Dialogue: 0,00:15:40.91,00:15:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这才是重要的部分  -在哪
Dialogue: 0,00:15:44.54,00:15:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问吧  每个人都在等  跟你们一样
Dialogue: 0,00:15:55.79,00:15:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文件
Dialogue: 0,00:16:11.50,00:16:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-晚上好  -给你的
Dialogue: 0,00:16:14.38,00:16:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲和的礼物
Dialogue: 0,00:16:18.66,00:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,00:16:22.07,00:16:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以放进箱子里
Dialogue: 0,00:16:30.71,00:16:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们找到你的方式
Dialogue: 0,00:16:33.62,00:16:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好意的礼物
Dialogue: 0,00:16:40.22,00:16:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,00:16:48.43,00:16:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,00:16:50.70,00:16:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很乐意帮忙
Dialogue: 0,00:16:56.30,00:16:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,00:17:43.75,00:17:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一向那么优雅
Dialogue: 0,00:17:53.51,00:17:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  库尔特夫人
Dialogue: 0,00:17:57.75,00:18:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是虫子的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,00:18:00.98,00:18:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑得到处都是
Dialogue: 0,00:18:02.59,00:18:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是你最该担心的
Dialogue: 0,00:18:04.83,00:18:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他派你来的吗
Dialogue: 0,00:18:06.75,00:18:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我跟着你上了意念机
Dialogue: 0,00:18:09.38,00:18:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来做探子  还是来帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,00:18:12.34,00:18:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,00:18:13.71,00:18:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  好让你把我的一举一动汇报给阿斯里尔吗
Dialogue: 0,00:18:16.07,00:18:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-得了吧  -我不能
Dialogue: 0,00:18:17.79,00:18:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃跑时  我的天然磁石共鸣器弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,00:18:21.55,00:18:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思  所以实际上是你需要我
Dialogue: 0,00:18:27.86,00:18:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想在他们杀了莱拉之前  杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,00:18:32.35,00:18:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们先杀了你呢
Dialogue: 0,00:18:35.87,00:18:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么轻易就那自己冒险
Dialogue: 0,00:18:38.42,00:18:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对这里有什么了解
Dialogue: 0,00:18:41.59,00:18:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,00:18:44.19,00:18:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧  你别无选择
Dialogue: 0,00:18:47.47,00:18:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有我  你用不了意念机
Dialogue: 0,00:18:49.50,00:18:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有意念机  你无法回到阿斯里尔那里
Dialogue: 0,00:18:54.43,00:18:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,00:18:57.14,00:18:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟踪了戈梅兹神父
Dialogue: 0,00:18:59.87,00:19:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎对一间屋子尤为关注
Dialogue: 0,00:20:14.34,00:20:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要继续走吗
Dialogue: 0,00:20:16.74,00:20:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们似乎应该继续走
Dialogue: 0,00:20:19.62,00:20:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在盯着看  是吧
Dialogue: 0,00:20:20.55,00:20:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  他们在盯着看  但什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,00:20:23.51,00:20:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就像置身于一部恐怖电影中
Dialogue: 0,00:20:26.06,00:20:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要看一部让你觉得恐怖的电影
Dialogue: 0,00:20:29.55,00:20:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有道理
Dialogue: 0,00:20:31.10,00:20:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我喜欢有熊的那部影片  -你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,00:20:36.11,00:20:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是旅人
Dialogue: 0,00:20:37.95,00:20:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去死人世界
Dialogue: 0,00:20:40.26,00:20:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  那我们同路
Dialogue: 0,00:20:48.11,00:20:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  我们不了解这里
Dialogue: 0,00:20:49.38,00:20:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又似乎有些善意
Dialogue: 0,00:20:52.43,00:20:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很想知道这里的规矩
Dialogue: 0,00:20:58.75,00:21:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  进来吧
Dialogue: 0,00:21:03.78,00:21:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,00:21:15.31,00:21:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,00:21:18.14,00:21:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介绍下自己吧
Dialogue: 0,00:21:20.22,00:21:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莱拉  这是威尔
Dialogue: 0,00:21:23.23,00:21:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会过多打扰大家
Dialogue: 0,00:21:26.27,00:21:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们在找我的朋友  他在死人世界
Dialogue: 0,00:21:29.07,00:21:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道这里是否属于死人世界
Dialogue: 0,00:21:30.27,00:21:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是怎么过去
Dialogue: 0,00:21:31.75,00:21:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有谁能告诉我们点情况
Dialogue: 0,00:21:34.03,00:21:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,00:21:36.02,00:21:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的死神怎么没告诉他们去哪
Dialogue: 0,00:21:38.06,00:21:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉瑞沙  他们是来求助的
Dialogue: 0,00:21:40.50,00:21:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不该需要帮助
Dialogue: 0,00:21:42.15,00:21:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-去问你们的死神  -我们没有死神
Dialogue: 0,00:21:44.78,00:21:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没死呢
Dialogue: 0,00:21:46.42,00:21:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  坐下
Dialogue: 0,00:21:59.10,00:22:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也没死呢  是吧
Dialogue: 0,00:22:01.51,00:22:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些等候区的人
Dialogue: 0,00:22:03.58,00:22:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的死神就在附近  引导我们
Dialogue: 0,00:22:08.99,00:22:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会欢迎它的  我们准备好了  但是...
Dialogue: 0,00:22:14.26,00:22:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它还没准备好带我们走
Dialogue: 0,00:22:16.15,00:22:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神是什么
Dialogue: 0,00:22:17.94,00:22:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,00:22:22.94,00:22:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都有死神
Dialogue: 0,00:22:25.03,00:22:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它如影随形  跟随每个人一生
Dialogue: 0,00:22:27.95,00:22:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有点吓人不
Dialogue: 0,00:22:29.07,00:22:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不会  亲爱的  这很自然
Dialogue: 0,00:22:34.50,00:22:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自你出生
Dialogue: 0,00:22:37.95,00:22:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死神便跟你一同来到这世上
Dialogue: 0,00:22:41.70,00:22:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是你的死神带你离开
Dialogue: 0,00:22:45.95,00:22:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一种爱
Dialogue: 0,00:22:48.31,00:22:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你能看到我们的死神吗  -不  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,00:22:51.91,00:22:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能看到我们自己的
Dialogue: 0,00:22:56.58,00:23:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你准备好了  据说那很美
Dialogue: 0,00:23:01.82,00:23:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死神说
Dialogue: 0,00:23:03.55,00:23:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"好了  孩子  跟我走吧"
Dialogue: 0,00:23:10.54,00:23:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就跟他们走
Dialogue: 0,00:23:12.63,00:23:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做船  见船夫
Dialogue: 0,00:23:16.10,00:23:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我梦里看到的
Dialogue: 0,00:23:18.15,00:23:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就得去那里
Dialogue: 0,00:23:20.11,00:23:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有你的死神  你们可去不了
Dialogue: 0,00:23:23.43,00:23:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能告诉我们它在哪  我们就不打扰你了
Dialogue: 0,00:23:25.31,00:23:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道它在哪  或是那一边有什么
Dialogue: 0,00:23:28.46,00:23:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人知道  因为没人回来过
Dialogue: 0,00:23:33.82,00:23:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们想渡湖
Dialogue: 0,00:23:36.66,00:23:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死人世界  就只能是跟你们自己的死神
Dialogue: 0,00:23:41.99,00:23:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请他们来找你们  友好客气地请他们来
Dialogue: 0,00:23:48.35,00:23:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会来的
Dialogue: 0,00:23:57.11,00:23:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐
Dialogue: 0,00:23:59.47,00:24:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要早餐  我得祈祷
Dialogue: 0,00:24:03.35,00:24:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡里的礼拜堂在哪
Dialogue: 0,00:24:13.95,00:24:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库尔特夫人  你应该待在你的房间里
Dialogue: 0,00:24:17.13,00:24:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我在找礼拜堂  我要赎罪
Dialogue: 0,00:24:20.43,00:24:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在房间里祈祷  跟在礼拜堂里祈祷一样的
Dialogue: 0,00:24:24.35,00:24:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我在权威者自己的房子里
Dialogue: 0,00:24:26.38,00:24:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更容易听到他的训导
Dialogue: 0,00:24:31.95,00:24:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要去礼拜堂
Dialogue: 0,00:24:33.98,00:24:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能在安排好的时间里去
Dialogue: 0,00:24:37.22,00:24:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,00:24:38.83,00:24:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我都来了
Dialogue: 0,00:24:39.72,00:24:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不介意我到处看看吧
Dialogue: 0,00:24:50.55,00:24:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他们没什么意思
Dialogue: 0,00:24:58.58,00:24:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不停下
Dialogue: 0,00:24:59.99,00:25:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就要怎么样
Dialogue: 0,00:25:05.06,00:25:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找人来
Dialogue: 0,00:25:06.99,00:25:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,00:25:09.22,00:25:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都需要人帮忙
Dialogue: 0,00:25:13.43,00:25:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,00:25:32.62,00:25:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-早上好  -早上好
Dialogue: 0,00:25:40.42,00:25:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库珀博士
Dialogue: 0,00:25:45.99,00:25:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,00:25:48.14,00:25:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到  你还有工作
Dialogue: 0,00:25:51.90,00:25:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上  能见到你还活着真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,00:25:55.51,00:25:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你死了呢
Dialogue: 0,00:25:59.46,00:26:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休·麦克费尔把我丢下的人才都笼络来了
Dialogue: 0,00:26:04.99,00:26:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,00:26:07.99,00:26:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里恐怕是禁区  库尔特夫人
Dialogue: 0,00:26:10.19,00:26:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库珀博士  你一直对我很好
Dialogue: 0,00:26:19.18,00:26:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要现在改变态度
Dialogue: 0,00:26:23.18,00:26:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前
Dialogue: 0,00:26:25.11,00:26:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也总对我很好
Dialogue: 0,00:26:27.83,00:26:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  主教
Dialogue: 0,00:26:30.19,00:26:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庭长神父和我  对彼此没有秘密
Dialogue: 0,00:26:34.15,00:26:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必担心
Dialogue: 0,00:26:37.11,00:26:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个共鸣舱  是吧
Dialogue: 0,00:26:42.47,00:26:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,00:26:44.23,00:26:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你使用了部分我们的精灵闸刀的设计
Dialogue: 0,00:26:45.99,00:26:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上  不止是一部分
Dialogue: 0,00:26:48.54,00:26:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会还在干这个
Dialogue: 0,00:26:55.19,00:26:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,00:26:57.98,00:26:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,00:27:00.83,00:27:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它读取什么
Dialogue: 0,00:27:03.15,00:27:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它读取的东西让它能...
Dialogue: 0,00:27:09.10,00:27:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库珀博士
Dialogue: 0,00:27:12.94,00:27:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在制造炸弹吗
Dialogue: 0,00:27:15.62,00:27:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你不懂  -我明白
Dialogue: 0,00:27:27.98,00:27:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是有指向的  它的指向如何确定
Dialogue: 0,00:27:34.38,00:27:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,权威者
Dialogue: 0,00:27:36.82,00:27:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是吧
Dialogue: 0,00:27:44.79,00:27:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们来了
Dialogue: 0,00:27:46.10,00:27:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来找我  不是你
Dialogue: 0,00:27:48.27,00:27:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,00:27:50.86,00:27:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在的情况真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,00:27:56.31,00:27:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈梅兹
Dialogue: 0,00:28:09.43,00:28:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱拉  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,00:28:12.79,00:28:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫我们把死神请来
Dialogue: 0,00:28:15.59,00:28:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许如果我进入读真理仪时
Dialogue: 0,00:28:17.99,00:28:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种心理状态  她就会出现
Dialogue: 0,00:28:21.47,00:28:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,00:28:25.46,00:28:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我们能谈谈吗
Dialogue: 0,00:28:29.43,00:28:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈什么  我们已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,00:28:31.38,00:28:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  但是  召唤死神
Dialogue: 0,00:28:34.75,00:28:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道那意味着什么吗  -当然不知道
Dialogue: 0,00:28:36.59,00:28:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们来都来了
Dialogue: 0,00:28:38.99,00:28:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-或许这么做不对  -但我们在做了
Dialogue: 0,00:28:42.50,00:28:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来这里就是为了这个
Dialogue: 0,00:28:44.31,00:28:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回头还不迟
Dialogue: 0,00:28:46.31,00:28:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以用刀找到回家的路
Dialogue: 0,00:28:49.34,00:28:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是我这边的吗
Dialogue: 0,00:28:51.75,00:28:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我就在你身边
Dialogue: 0,00:28:57.75,00:28:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都不懂  是吧
Dialogue: 0,00:28:59.67,00:29:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没来得及跟罗杰道别
Dialogue: 0,00:29:02.23,00:29:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没来得及说"对不起"
Dialogue: 0,00:29:04.67,00:29:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想尽力做出弥补
Dialogue: 0,00:29:07.55,00:29:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕为此我要死
Dialogue: 0,00:29:10.95,00:29:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱拉
Dialogue: 0,00:29:13.98,00:29:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她来了
Dialogue: 0,00:29:23.19,00:29:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的死神
Dialogue: 0,00:29:26.29,00:29:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,00:29:28.35,00:29:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要来带我走吗
Dialogue: 0,00:29:30.87,00:29:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找我  我就来了
Dialogue: 0,00:29:36.67,00:29:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要单独跟她谈谈
Dialogue: 0,00:29:39.63,00:29:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不见你在跟谁说话
Dialogue: 0,00:29:42.18,00:29:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  她是我的
Dialogue: 0,00:29:49.47,00:29:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,00:29:53.07,00:29:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就回来  别担心
Dialogue: 0,00:30:20.42,00:30:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,权威者
Dialogue: 0,00:30:23.18,00:30:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你回应我的祈祷
Dialogue: 0,00:30:31.63,00:30:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予我赢得这场战争的手段
Dialogue: 0,00:30:42.30,00:30:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你的爱
Dialogue: 0,00:30:46.12,00:30:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和引导
Dialogue: 0,00:30:49.62,00:30:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给我行必要之事的力量
Dialogue: 0,00:30:56.78,00:30:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引领我们获得救赎
Dialogue: 0,00:31:06.67,00:31:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上他
Dialogue: 0,00:31:19.28,00:31:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这头发
Dialogue: 0,00:31:20.58,00:31:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能确定是那孩子的
Dialogue: 0,00:31:23.43,00:31:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉·帕维尔确定
Dialogue: 0,00:31:28.51,00:31:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了吗  库珀博士
Dialogue: 0,00:31:32.47,00:31:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够了
Dialogue: 0,00:31:35.54,00:31:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多快能准备好
Dialogue: 0,00:31:38.43,00:31:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几天内
Dialogue: 0,00:31:42.26,00:31:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  戈梅兹神父  这就可以了
Dialogue: 0,00:31:54.95,00:31:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定  一旦启动
Dialogue: 0,00:31:57.99,00:32:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹必会找到那女孩
Dialogue: 0,00:32:00.50,00:32:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都是独特的
Dialogue: 0,00:32:03.47,00:32:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们蕴含着密码  电脉冲
Dialogue: 0,00:32:06.71,00:32:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用这个
Dialogue: 0,00:32:09.18,00:32:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来瞄准装置
Dialogue: 0,00:32:11.15,00:32:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这头发  不管它在哪  都想重归整体
Dialogue: 0,00:32:17.22,00:32:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会不惜一切地追逐
Dialogue: 0,00:32:22.71,00:32:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那女孩在哪
Dialogue: 0,00:32:25.55,00:32:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管她在哪个世界
Dialogue: 0,00:32:28.03,00:32:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我的异端邪说
Dialogue: 0,00:32:30.27,00:32:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹都能找到莱拉
Dialogue: 0,00:32:54.75,00:32:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在吗
Dialogue: 0,00:32:59.23,00:33:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是时出现时消失
Dialogue: 0,00:33:02.55,00:33:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在
Dialogue: 0,00:33:05.27,00:33:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这辈子一直跟着你
Dialogue: 0,00:33:10.39,00:33:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个特别  忠心的朋友
Dialogue: 0,00:33:12.27,00:33:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生命的每时每刻我都在你身边
Dialogue: 0,00:33:16.43,00:33:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比任何人都了解你
Dialogue: 0,00:33:19.46,00:33:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,00:33:22.02,00:33:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至比你自己都了解你
Dialogue: 0,00:33:26.07,00:33:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要做个交易
Dialogue: 0,00:33:29.43,00:33:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恐怕不能做交易
Dialogue: 0,00:33:33.71,00:33:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我还没死
Dialogue: 0,00:33:35.83,00:33:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我需要去死人世界
Dialogue: 0,00:33:37.42,00:33:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要去那里见个人  然后回来
Dialogue: 0,00:33:42.79,00:33:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能帮我吗
Dialogue: 0,00:33:44.83,00:33:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子  你最终
Dialogue: 0,00:33:46.07,00:33:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会毫不费力地到达死人世界
Dialogue: 0,00:33:49.86,00:33:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有风险
Dialogue: 0,00:33:52.10,00:33:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一段安全  平静的旅程
Dialogue: 0,00:33:55.30,00:33:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要急着冲过去
Dialogue: 0,00:33:58.87,00:34:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须去
Dialogue: 0,00:34:01.47,00:34:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔也是
Dialogue: 0,00:34:04.62,00:34:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们身边都有离开得太早的人
Dialogue: 0,00:34:06.67,00:34:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都需要做出弥补
Dialogue: 0,00:34:08.47,00:34:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都希望可以跟故去的人说说话
Dialogue: 0,00:34:11.94,00:34:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要为你破例
Dialogue: 0,00:34:16.14,00:34:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,00:34:18.55,00:34:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你这辈子都跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,00:34:21.83,00:34:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早知道我会提出来
Dialogue: 0,00:34:24.91,00:34:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的一直跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,00:34:27.70,00:34:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,00:34:30.10,00:34:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟随了你
Dialogue: 0,00:34:33.26,00:34:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见到了你的选择
Dialogue: 0,00:34:40.75,00:34:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到他死了吗
Dialogue: 0,00:34:42.71,00:34:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗杰
Dialogue: 0,00:34:47.14,00:34:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,00:34:53.47,00:34:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想做超凡的人
Dialogue: 0,00:34:57.43,00:34:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许曾经是的
Dialogue: 0,00:35:01.03,00:35:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父母  他们只想着那个
Dialogue: 0,00:35:05.55,00:35:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想做个好人
Dialogue: 0,00:35:07.39,00:35:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想帮助别人
Dialogue: 0,00:35:10.26,00:35:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗杰需要我
Dialogue: 0,00:35:12.03,00:35:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他上次需要我时  我没有帮到他
Dialogue: 0,00:35:16.87,00:35:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我
Dialogue: 0,00:35:20.02,00:35:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的心
Dialogue: 0,00:35:24.18,00:35:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,00:35:30.35,00:35:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会指引你  莱拉·巧舌如簧
Dialogue: 0,00:35:34.67,00:35:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你去
Dialogue: 0,00:35:37.66,00:35:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你到了
Dialogue: 0,00:35:40.39,00:35:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一边不是我能去的
Dialogue: 0,00:35:44.43,00:35:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以怎么出来
Dialogue: 0,00:35:46.79,00:35:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只能自己想办法了
Dialogue: 0,00:36:44.10,00:36:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,00:37:17.15,00:37:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,00:37:18.05,00:37:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,00:37:40.38,00:37:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了
Dialogue: 0,00:37:42.70,00:37:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还...
Dialogue: 0,00:37:44.51,00:37:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在附近吗  对
Dialogue: 0,00:37:47.59,00:37:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么说的
Dialogue: 0,00:37:49.74,00:37:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能看到我的死神吗
Dialogue: 0,00:37:51.90,00:37:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不到他的死神吧
Dialogue: 0,00:37:53.59,00:37:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到  他也看不到
Dialogue: 0,00:37:56.55,00:37:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得准备好了  才会看到死神
Dialogue: 0,00:37:59.78,00:38:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等时候到了才行
Dialogue: 0,00:38:02.59,00:38:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你  在合适的时候才能看到死神
Dialogue: 0,00:38:08.63,00:38:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的死神会带我们去湖附近
Dialogue: 0,00:38:10.98,00:38:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你准备好了
Dialogue: 0,00:38:13.39,00:38:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我准备好了吗  -希望是的
Dialogue: 0,00:38:16.82,00:38:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你准备好
Dialogue: 0,00:38:24.74,00:38:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总带我去最棒的地方  知道吗
Dialogue: 0,00:39:09.38,00:39:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,00:39:28.35,00:39:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还需要做什么
Dialogue: 0,00:40:00.54,00:40:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来保护她的
Dialogue: 0,00:40:01.71,00:40:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却给了他们炸弹的引线
Dialogue: 0,00:40:04.91,00:40:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自大
Dialogue: 0,00:40:07.98,00:40:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太自大了  我低估了他们
Dialogue: 0,00:40:12.30,00:40:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得走了  回阿斯里尔那里去
Dialogue: 0,00:40:14.79,00:40:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一旦他知道了他们在干什么  -他会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,00:40:20.03,00:40:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能
Dialogue: 0,00:40:22.92,00:40:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会插手的
Dialogue: 0,00:40:25.87,00:40:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,00:41:08.42,00:41:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,00:41:11.38,00:41:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确是想在他们杀了她之前杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,00:41:16.14,00:41:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会让他们再有机会了
Dialogue: 0,00:41:19.27,00:41:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经让他们的炸弹发不出去了
Dialogue: 0,00:41:24.34,00:41:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们得回去  -不
Dialogue: 0,00:41:27.83,00:41:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还会想别的办法  一个不行下一个
Dialogue: 0,00:41:33.07,00:41:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须现在就阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,00:41:41.19,00:41:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得找到意念机
Dialogue: 0,00:41:44.46,00:41:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,00:41:48.35,00:41:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭
Dialogue: 0,00:42:05.18,00:42:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每一步都走得更慢了  你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,00:42:08.55,00:42:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在改主意还不迟
Dialogue: 0,00:42:09.98,00:42:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想改主意
Dialogue: 0,00:42:11.98,00:42:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈以前总说  "你不解决就不算解决了"
Dialogue: 0,00:42:17.39,00:42:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想来  也没关系  我可以自己去
Dialogue: 0,00:42:20.14,00:42:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找了你几个月
Dialogue: 0,00:42:21.75,00:42:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了在地狱门口跟你道别
Dialogue: 0,00:42:24.02,00:42:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那不是地狱  看上去挺像  但不是
Dialogue: 0,00:42:28.42,00:42:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我只想确定你确定  -我确定
Dialogue: 0,00:42:30.22,00:42:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时我们做一些事  到了一些地方
Dialogue: 0,00:42:31.98,00:42:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就忘了是怎么到的了
Dialogue: 0,00:42:33.10,00:42:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我怎么到这儿的  威尔
Dialogue: 0,00:42:35.71,00:42:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们回不来了呢
Dialogue: 0,00:42:38.55,00:42:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就是为做一件重要的事而死
Dialogue: 0,00:43:02.34,00:43:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,00:43:18.70,00:43:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,00:43:22.31,00:43:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,00:43:28.11,00:43:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-站住  -站住
Dialogue: 0,00:43:31.62,00:43:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,00:43:34.42,00:43:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意念机就在前面
Dialogue: 0,00:43:38.94,00:43:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在这里
Dialogue: 0,00:43:51.99,00:43:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我没让人监视你吗
Dialogue: 0,00:43:58.50,00:44:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别无选择  玛丽莎
Dialogue: 0,00:44:00.97,00:44:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是要杀了她
Dialogue: 0,00:44:03.99,00:44:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管我做什么
Dialogue: 0,00:44:05.67,00:44:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事
Dialogue: 0,00:44:07.39,00:44:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我别无选择
Dialogue: 0,00:44:10.10,00:44:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我有话要说
Dialogue: 0,00:44:13.99,00:44:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为谋杀斯特罗克主教受审
Dialogue: 0,00:44:19.38,00:44:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你们的庭长神父共谋杀害了他
Dialogue: 0,00:44:22.59,00:44:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此人每个毛孔都透着罪孽
Dialogue: 0,00:44:28.02,00:44:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒谎
Dialogue: 0,00:44:29.43,00:44:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我说的是实话
Dialogue: 0,00:44:32.74,00:44:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当着训诫法庭
Dialogue: 0,00:44:34.42,00:44:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会这么说
Dialogue: 0,00:44:36.63,00:44:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没你说话的份
Dialogue: 0,00:44:39.34,00:44:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个荡妇
Dialogue: 0,00:44:40.35,00:44:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总想要不属于自己的东西
Dialogue: 0,00:44:42.11,00:44:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫被你的情人  异端者阿斯里尔所杀
Dialogue: 0,00:44:45.91,00:44:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的私生子被遗弃
Dialogue: 0,00:44:48.98,00:44:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到她变成了罪孽本身
Dialogue: 0,00:44:52.13,00:44:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改变了  你可没有  休
Dialogue: 0,00:44:54.51,00:44:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得有人阻止你
Dialogue: 0,00:44:55.67,00:44:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"休"  "休"是谁
Dialogue: 0,00:44:57.91,00:45:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是庭长神父  你要称我...
Dialogue: 0,00:45:02.07,00:45:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为"庭长神父"
Dialogue: 0,00:45:05.15,00:45:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或"阁下"
Dialogue: 0,00:45:08.54,00:45:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,00:45:10.55,00:45:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,00:45:13.07,00:45:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就忠于他吗
Dialogue: 0,00:45:16.43,00:45:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是天上那位
Dialogue: 0,00:45:19.30,00:45:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真理  而是权力吗
Dialogue: 0,00:45:22.19,00:45:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我失望  戈梅兹神父
Dialogue: 0,00:45:24.27,00:45:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她走
Dialogue: 0,00:45:25.06,00:45:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你们不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,00:45:27.38,00:45:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还自称神职人员
Dialogue: 0,00:45:29.43,00:45:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得权威者现在会怎么看你
Dialogue: 0,00:45:32.59,00:45:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个充满仇恨之人  周围都是崇拜你的仇恨之人
Dialogue: 0,00:45:36.35,00:45:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个猪猡神父
Dialogue: 0,00:45:37.91,00:45:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-别让她说了  -恶心
Dialogue: 0,00:45:41.82,00:45:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,00:45:43.98,00:45:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡言乱语  情绪激动的女人
Dialogue: 0,00:45:47.54,00:45:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有人相信你
Dialogue: 0,00:45:49.98,00:45:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一句话都说不清楚
Dialogue: 0,00:45:54.43,00:45:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如此美丽
Dialogue: 0,00:45:56.79,00:46:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美得诱人
Dialogue: 0,00:46:00.90,00:46:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要给你的美  补上它一直欠缺的东西
Dialogue: 0,00:46:07.31,00:46:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩典[优雅]
Dialogue: 0,00:46:09.99,00:46:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你怎么拿走头发的
Dialogue: 0,00:46:13.42,00:46:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你没全拿走
Dialogue: 0,00:46:15.71,00:46:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还剩足够多
Dialogue: 0,00:46:18.11,00:46:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以达成目的
Dialogue: 0,00:46:20.31,00:46:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们切开你的精灵
Dialogue: 0,00:46:25.06,00:46:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将成为子弹
Dialogue: 0,00:46:27.71,00:46:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死莱拉·贝拉克瓦
Dialogue: 0,00:46:32.63,00:46:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我们免于罪孽
Dialogue: 0,00:46:45.31,00:46:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她去地窖
Dialogue: 0,00:46:47.94,00:46:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她的精灵抓来给我
Dialogue: 0,00:47:52.94,00:47:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,00:47:54.79,00:47:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴你们能来
Dialogue: 0,00:47:57.43,00:48:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下一切物品  上船吧
Dialogue: 0,00:48:06.10,00:48:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能明白吗
Dialogue: 0,00:48:27.30,00:48:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们需要渡河  -对不起
Dialogue: 0,00:48:30.35,00:48:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们中的一位不能渡河
Dialogue: 0,00:48:34.47,00:48:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一位吗
Dialogue: 0,00:48:40.27,00:48:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不  那...  -我们必须遵守规矩
Dialogue: 0,00:48:43.10,00:48:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是必要的痛苦  他不能渡河
Dialogue: 0,00:48:47.67,00:48:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但他就是我  -你要来  他就得留下
Dialogue: 0,00:48:51.54,00:48:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你不懂  如果我们分开  我们会死
Dialogue: 0,00:48:55.84,00:48:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那不正是你想要的吗
Dialogue: 0,00:49:08.31,00:49:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这不对  我又不会留下我的一部分
Dialogue: 0,00:49:11.03,00:49:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-凭什么她要这么做  -你会的
Dialogue: 0,00:49:13.47,00:49:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当然会
Dialogue: 0,00:49:16.59,00:49:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于她来说  幸运或不幸的是
Dialogue: 0,00:49:18.73,00:49:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能看到她要留下的部分  跟他说话
Dialogue: 0,00:49:22.79,00:49:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你要到湖上才会知道  到那时
Dialogue: 0,00:49:25.78,00:49:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运或不幸的是
Dialogue: 0,00:49:27.55,00:49:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经来不及做什么了
Dialogue: 0,00:49:31.02,00:49:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们都要把自己的那部分留下
Dialogue: 0,00:49:34.42,00:49:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规矩很清楚
Dialogue: 0,00:49:39.22,00:49:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会上船的  别担心
Dialogue: 0,00:49:41.87,00:49:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱拉  你没听他说吗  他不许
Dialogue: 0,00:49:44.54,00:49:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...在渡河时陪伴你们
Dialogue: 0,00:49:47.46,00:49:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  他可以上船  他坐在哪都行
Dialogue: 0,00:49:51.30,00:49:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去哪都一起
Dialogue: 0,00:49:52.42,00:49:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没人对此有任何异议
Dialogue: 0,00:49:53.82,00:49:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不明白怎么就...  -他可以上船
Dialogue: 0,00:49:55.23,00:49:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果他上船  船就不走了
Dialogue: 0,00:49:58.62,00:50:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用这个划吗  我可以来划
Dialogue: 0,00:50:00.74,00:50:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我能划船
Dialogue: 0,00:50:08.82,00:50:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,00:50:15.14,00:50:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能分开
Dialogue: 0,00:50:17.46,00:50:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能
Dialogue: 0,00:50:19.71,00:50:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘
Dialogue: 0,00:50:21.55,00:50:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  潘
Dialogue: 0,00:50:24.98,00:50:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你赌上了一切
Dialogue: 0,00:50:26.18,00:50:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她什么时候能再见到他
Dialogue: 0,00:50:28.11,00:50:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}求你  潘
Dialogue: 0,00:50:28.74,00:50:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她见不到了
Dialogue: 0,00:50:30.03,00:50:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你怎么能确定这么做是对的
Dialogue: 0,00:50:32.63,00:50:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走后  还从这里回来吗
Dialogue: 0,00:50:35.06,00:50:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带过成千上万人渡湖
Dialogue: 0,00:50:37.42,00:50:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}相信我  潘  求你
Dialogue: 0,00:50:37.59,00:50:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人回来过
Dialogue: 0,00:50:39.87,00:50:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们都到这一步了
Dialogue: 0,00:50:40.36,00:50:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会回来
Dialogue: 0,00:50:40.83,00:50:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们可能会丧命
Dialogue: 0,00:50:42.91,00:50:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不了解莱拉  也不了解我
Dialogue: 0,00:50:44.31,00:50:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们会找到办法  别的门路
Dialogue: 0,00:50:46.79,00:50:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我们要回来  行行好吧  船夫
Dialogue: 0,00:50:49.37,00:50:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-让她带上精灵吧  -这不是你们能打破的规矩
Dialogue: 0,00:50:54.66,00:50:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是法律
Dialogue: 0,00:50:56.98,00:50:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这个
Dialogue: 0,00:50:58.19,00:50:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那晚在山上
Dialogue: 0,00:50:59.54,00:51:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们不能这么做  莱拉
Dialogue: 0,00:51:02.19,00:51:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能抖抖手  让水往上走
Dialogue: 0,00:51:05.63,00:51:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能带她的精灵去死人世界
Dialogue: 0,00:51:09.03,00:51:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这次或许得破个例了
Dialogue: 0,00:51:13.79,00:51:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那一切都不是罗杰的错  可我都没能跟他道别
Dialogue: 0,00:51:15.83,00:51:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得渡人多久了
Dialogue: 0,00:51:21.34,00:51:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得如果有什么伤得了我
Dialogue: 0,00:51:22.99,00:51:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人不会已经做了吗
Dialogue: 0,00:51:24.75,00:51:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我渡的人  都乐意跟我走吗
Dialogue: 0,00:51:27.90,00:51:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他们挣扎  哭闹  贿赂
Dialogue: 0,00:51:29.70,00:51:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威胁  抗争  都不好用
Dialogue: 0,00:51:33.87,00:51:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我不想这么做
Dialogue: 0,00:51:36.51,00:51:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}如果还有别的办法能弥补...
Dialogue: 0,00:51:38.18,00:51:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐呵和顺从能让事情好办点
Dialogue: 0,00:51:44.31,00:51:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我两样兼备
Dialogue: 0,00:51:47.26,00:51:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我劝你也这样
Dialogue: 0,00:51:52.55,00:51:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你怎么能确定这样是对的
Dialogue: 0,00:51:57.26,00:51:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  真的
Dialogue: 0,00:52:00.47,00:52:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果她要来  就得自己来
Dialogue: 0,00:52:04.14,00:52:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想丢下你
Dialogue: 0,00:52:06.82,00:52:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还能回头
Dialogue: 0,00:52:09.15,00:52:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能不去
Dialogue: 0,00:52:10.90,00:52:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你可以  莱拉  -那罗杰呢
Dialogue: 0,00:52:13.87,00:52:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有塞尔
Dialogue: 0,00:52:15.95,00:52:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都没能长大
Dialogue: 0,00:52:17.91,00:52:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在不是罗杰和塞尔
Dialogue: 0,00:52:20.35,00:52:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗杰死了  塞尔不在了
Dialogue: 0,00:52:24.23,00:52:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不再是莱拉和潘了  你要撇下我
Dialogue: 0,00:52:29.79,00:52:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,00:52:32.18,00:52:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但我们的梦  -我没做那个梦
Dialogue: 0,00:52:35.26,00:52:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的梦  我根本不想来
Dialogue: 0,00:52:38.70,00:52:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的选择
Dialogue: 0,00:52:41.47,00:52:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们是一起的
Dialogue: 0,00:52:42.94,00:52:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你这么做我们就不能在一起了
Dialogue: 0,00:52:44.99,00:52:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你
Dialogue: 0,00:52:47.43,00:52:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能背叛罗杰
Dialogue: 0,00:52:49.79,00:52:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的死是我的错  现在他需要我
Dialogue: 0,00:52:52.71,00:52:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也需要你
Dialogue: 0,00:52:54.62,00:52:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么就不明白
Dialogue: 0,00:52:58.51,00:53:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我去哪  -我一定找到你
Dialogue: 0,00:53:03.58,00:53:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去死人世界
Dialogue: 0,00:53:04.83,00:53:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我会回来  找到你
Dialogue: 0,00:53:08.07,00:53:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会丢下你的
Dialogue: 0,00:53:11.02,00:53:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会丢下你的
Dialogue: 0,00:53:12.71,00:53:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是永别
Dialogue: 0,00:53:14.51,00:53:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威尔和我会找到离开的路
Dialogue: 0,00:53:16.62,00:53:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们去找阿斯里尔
Dialogue: 0,00:53:18.30,00:53:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也得想办法去  但我必须这么做
Dialogue: 0,00:53:23.70,00:53:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你已经拿定主意了
Dialogue: 0,00:53:26.87,00:53:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选了罗杰而不是我
Dialogue: 0,00:53:28.22,00:53:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  潘  求你  别这样
Dialogue: 0,00:53:31.30,00:53:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你
Dialogue: 0,00:53:35.74,00:53:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你  没别的办法了  我必须这么做
Dialogue: 0,00:53:47.87,00:53:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,00:53:51.67,00:53:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,00:55:24.15,00:55:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心